txt.en: Gandalf the Grey has summoned you to meet him at the Prancing Pony in Bree to discuss matters which concern him.

'Ah, [placeholder], it is good that you have come. Shadows are rising quickly in the East, as the Enemy prepares to unleash his evil upon Middle-earth once more.\n\n'We have much to discuss, you and I, ere we move against the Shadow in the East.'
